Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Combine dressing, 1/2 cup of the mozzarella cheese, the Parmesan cheese, broccoli and pimientos. Spread into baking dish or 9-inch pie plate. Bake 20 to 25 min. or until heated through. Sprinkle with remaining 1/2 cup mozzarella cheese. Continue baking 5 min. or until mozzarella cheese is melted. Serve with the crackers.